		<div
			class="peer relative box-border flex h-6 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-solid border-theme-base-900 bg-theme-base-100 after:absolute after:start-[0.105em] after:top-[0.105em] after:h-[1.225rem] after:w-[1.225rem] after:rounded-full after:border after:border-theme-base-100 after:bg-theme-base-900 after:transition-all after:content-[''] peer-checked:after:translate-x-full dark:border-theme-base-100 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:after:border-slate-700 dark:after:bg-theme-base-100"
		>
			<svg
				class="theme-icon moon scale-75"
